# Favicon PNG Generation Instructions

This file should be replaced with a 32x32 PNG favicon generated from the SVG.

To generate the PNG file:

1. Use the SVG favicon.svg file in this directory
2. Convert it to PNG format at 32x32 pixels
3. Ensure it maintains the fuchsia to purple gradient
4. Replace this file with the generated PNG

The SVG favicon is already properly configured and will work in modern browsers. 